  "keyFeatures": [
    "ECMAScript 2023+ compliance with ongoing spec support",
    "Small footprint with embeddable C API",
    "Module system with ES6 import/export",
    "Runtime and context isolation with shared objects",
    "Bytecode compilation and standalone executables",
    "Cross-platform support (Linux, macOS, Windows, WASI)",
    "Standard library with file I/O, networking, and workers",
    "Memory limits and execution timeout control"
